t: Huquq al-insan fi al-yahudiyah wa-al-masihiyah wa-al-islam muqaranatan bi-al-qanun al-duwali
Al-wasit al-idari : sharh qanun majlis al-dawlah fi daw' al-fiqh wa-al-qada' wa-ahkam al-mahkamah al-idariyah al-'ulya.al-juz' al-rabi'
Al-wasit al-idari : mawsu'at al-mas'uliyah al-idariyah fi daw' al-qada' wa-al-fiqh wa-ahkam al-mahkamah al-idariyah al-'ulya.al-juz' al-th'n'
Dirasah naqdiyah lil-itar al-qanuni lil-jarauim al-iliktruniyah fi al-aradi al-filastiniyah
'Uqud al-binau wa-al-muqawalat al-saghirah fi filastin bayna qusur al-nazariyah wa-ishkalat al-tatbiq
Al-ishkaliyah al-q'nn'yah f' haqq taqrir masir iqlim 'arabistan
Al-thalathunat fi al-qadaya al-fiqhiayh al-mu'asirah : dirasah muqaranah li-ahamm al-masauil al-tibbiyah wa-al-maliyah wa-al-ijtima'iyah
Haqq al-tajammu' wa-al-tanzim fi al-duwal al-'arabiyah : madkhal islah wa-tanmiyah
Dawr muqaddimat al-dasatir fi al-tafsir al-dusturi : dirasah muqaranah
Al-masuuliyah al-jinauiyah 'an al-akhtau al-tibbiyah fi majal al-tawlid
Al-masuuliyah al-jinauiyah lil-qauimin bi-a'mal al-binau : dirasah muqaranah
Al-'uqud al-idariyah ma bayna al-ilzam al-qanuni wa-al-waqi' al-'amali : dirasah muqaranah mahalliyah wa-dawliyah
Al-ittifaq al-ijraui fi qanun al-murafa'at al-madaniyah wa-al-tijariyah
Istiqlal al-qadau : haqq al-insan fi al-lujuu ila qadau mustaqil
Mafhum al-karamah al-insaniyah fi al-qadau al-dusturi : dirasah tahliliyah tausiliyah muqaranah
